1024
01:36:42,963 --> 01:36:46,091
Actually a regular coffee would be great.

1025
01:36:47,927 --> 01:36:49,345
Thanks.

1026
01:36:58,604 --> 01:37:01,982
- There you go. - Thank you, much needed..

1027
01:37:04,276 --> 01:37:07,780
Hey.. I missed you.

1028
01:37:07,780 --> 01:37:09,448
I missed you, too.

1029
01:37:10,324 --> 01:37:12,743
How have things been here? Busy?

1030
01:37:12,785 --> 01:37:14,995
- Yeah, good. - Yeah?

1031
01:37:15,037 --> 01:37:17,748
No uh, you know, Mr. Trumps coming in or anything..

1032
01:37:17,790 --> 01:37:24,171
Oh right, no, no ones throwing down Benjamin's?

1033
01:37:24,213 --> 01:37:26,966
Those days are over, I guess.

1034
01:37:26,966 --> 01:37:30,469
